You may have probably never heard this story, but 
when I was in office, their athletic budget was in

06:31.632 --> 06:39.140
huge trouble. She had borrowed, I think, several 
million dollars out of the student activity and

06:41.142 --> 06:53.174
the state auditor that was on their way out. So she 
