12:42.227 --> 12:47.756
this is probably saying the same thing. What did 
you learn at A&M that has had a strong effect on your

12:47.796 --> 12:53.184
life? Well, I think the things that I just related. 
I think hard work, integrity,

13:09.477 --> 13:12.189
I guess comradeship to a certain extent. But I 
think those, I think.

