their own success may be their own failure

14:57.344 --> 15:01.851
ultimately. They're going to have to recognize 
that Hispanic population, especially in

15:02.624 --> 15:08.751
relation to Austin and Washington. And I don't 
know. I think once they become more diverse down

15:10.252 --> 15:15.818
there, they're going to start having problems 
they haven't had before. And I don't think you're

